  "method": [
    "In a large frying pan heat the olive oil and then add the diced onion.",
    "Next add the crushed garlic and diced red chili and fry for another",
    "minute.",
    "Finally add the beef mince and turn the heat up.",
    "Add the taco spice mix and some seasoning and continue to fry the",
    "mince.",
    "Add the mixture in each tortilla.",
    "Take each tortilla and neatly trim the edges so they are square.",
    "Add grated cheese on top.",
    "Bake them for thirty minutes.",
    "Add cilantro on top and serve immediately."
